NCAA MEN'S 3RD & 4TH ROUND REGIONALS: AUSTIN
March 27, 2005
Kelenna Azubuike
Chuck Hayes
Tubby Smith
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT








<p>	Q.  Chuck, can you just describe what you guys were going through while you were waiting for the decision about Patrick's shot and what you thought during that time?</p>
<p>	Q.  Chuck, during the time you were waiting, what was that like?</p>
<p>	Q.  In the first overtime you got ahead by four and then that sequence when they got five offensive rebounds and Brown hits it three, how important was that to the outcome?</p>
